<p>Your clients will love the [_1] trading platform because we offer a complete trading experience tailored to the needs of an exceptionally wide range of traders.</p>
<p>Novice traders can use our intuitive visual platform to learn about trading, practice trading and gain trading experience.</p>
<p>Seasoned traders can use the [_1] platform for the full advantage of the wide range of trading and analysis tools we have on offer.</p>", broker_name) %]

<h3>[% l("Why should I become a binary options trading affiliate?") %]</h3>
[% l("<p>In only a short space of time since their inception, binary options are fast becoming a popular trading product. The numerous binary options trading platforms subsequently being created support this growing trend. By becoming an affiliate now you can profit from the fast growth of interest in this new industry.</p>
<p>Binary options trading is a high profit market where there's a place for everyone ~[including you~] to take a cut of the pie!</p>") %]

<h3>[% l("Why should I become a [_1] affiliate?", broker_name) %]</h3>

[% l("<ul class='bullet'>
<li>[_1] is the leading binary option trading platform.</li>
<li>With an interface in English, Spanish, French, Japanese, Portuguese, Russian and Indonesian it has an internationally wide appeal.</li>
<li>The [_1] platform is 100% web based making it instantly available for clients.</li>
<li>The platform is user friendly and accessible to all levels of traders.</li>
<li>The [_1] affiliate program is competitive and adaptive to your unique requirements ~[whatever they may be~].</li>
</ul>
<p>If you want to profit from this high demand product then your best option is to partner with the market leader; [_1]. We've been in the business since 1999, and we know what we're doing.</p>", broker_name) %]

