<p>[% l("No. There's no cost to sign up to the [_1] affiliate program.", broker_name) %]</p>

<h3>[% l("Can I become a [_1] affiliate even if I don't have a website?", broker_name) %]</h3>
<p>[% l('Yes. Please email us at <a href="mailto:[_1]">[_1]</a> for further assistance.', affiliate_email) %]</p>

